snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Sister Location VR Anniversary
snippet.description:
It's been a whole year since I started this project and I wanted to thank you all for the wonderful support throughout development. Without you all, the game wouldn't have turned out the way it is now.

Here's a short little video I made showing progress from the very first version to now to celebrate the games anniversary.

GameJolt Page: https://gamejolt.com#/games/FnafSLVR/438011
Itch.io Page: https://yurogamedev.itch.io/fnafslvr
Discord Server: https://discord.gg/PMh8skn
